public opinion</link> on issues related to politics, policy and sensitive topics around the globe, and tracks democratic processes on a daily basis. It counts with a large archive of over 16,000 polls, more than 330 analysis articles, and more than 300 <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../457/9457.xml">
election</link> reviews.<p>

